<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.1">
<l>eṉṉātaṉ tēvikkaṉ ṟiṉpappū vīyātāḷ</l>
<l>taṉnātaṉ kāṇavē taṇpū marattiṉai</l>
<l>vaṉṉātap puḷḷāl valiyap paṟittiṭṭa</l>
<l>veṉṉātaṉ vaṉmaiyaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">vempirāṉ vaṉmaiyaip pāṭippaṟa.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the strength of my lord who</l>
<l>spontaneously plucked the tree of fresh flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">with [the help of his] strong, loud bird</l>
<l>while the lord of her who would not give the flower of love</l>
<l rend="indent">to the goddess of my lord looked on that day.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the strength of our master!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
